# Geological Material Name Type — SKOS ConceptScheme
# Generated from NameTypes.xlsx (sheets: Concept Scheme, Concepts, Namespeces, Agents)
# Generated: 2026-04-19
#
# Notes / data issues flagged during generation:
#  1. The "Namespeces" sheet maps prefix `gmnts` to
#     https://vocab.geospecimens.org/def/geological-material-name-types (plural "types"),
#     but all concept IRIs in the Concepts sheet use .../geological-material-name-type/<slug>
#     (singular + slash). Below, the concept base prefix is set to the singular-with-slash
#     form so concepts can be written compactly. Update the source sheet if desired.
#  2. The "Concept Scheme" sheet uses property `regstatus:derivationMode`, but no such
#     prefix is declared. Emitted below as `reg:derivationMode` (from the linked-data
#     registry vocabulary), which is the likely intended property.
#  3. The concept "structural-group" declares skos:broader of .../group-name, but no
#     concept with that IRI exists in this vocabulary (there is .../group). The reference
#     is transcribed faithfully; this is flagged below near the concept declaration.

@prefix dcat:      <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#> .
@prefix dcterms:   <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix isoroles:  <http://def.isotc211.org/iso19115-1/2014/CitationAndResponsiblePartyInformation/code/CI_RoleCode/> .
@prefix owl:       <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix prov:      <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#> .
@prefix rdf:       <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:      <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
